    <briefdescription>
<para>System that handles entity behavior when colliding with level boundaries. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This system checks if entities with movement components have exceeded the level bounds. When an entity leaves the bounds, it applies bounce behavior based on the LevelBoundsBehaviorComponent&apos;s restitution coefficient. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
